KNOW ALL MEN BY THESE PRESENTS:
That Cameo Palms Association, by and through its Board of Directors, does hereby claim a lien
against the real property legally described as follows:
Parcel #
200-58-683
The owner of the Property is:
Address
Edward Chernay
14225 Newcastle Drive, Sun City, AZ 85351
Lot 313 Tract # L, SUN CITY_UNIT 15-C_according to the plat recorded in the office of the County
Recorder of Maricopa County, Arizona, in Book 128 of Maps, at Page 16.
The lot owner currently owes $296.88 in delinquent assessments and fees and other charges

to pay future assessments, fees, attorney fees and other charges.
